Class AlignerHelper.Subproblem

java.lang.Object
org.biojava.nbio.alignment.routines.AlignerHelper.Subproblem
Enclosing class:
AlignerHelper
public static class AlignerHelper.Subproblem extends Object
Alignment subproblem. The bounds of the subproblem are the indicies representing the inclusive bounds of the dynamic programming alignment problem.
Author:
Daniel Cameron
